data.text: @laurakirsop I’m not a member at a gym at the mo, but I liked the treadmill too - I got into a bit of a meditative state with it! Are you doing a couch to 10k app or anything like that?
@laurakirsop Oooh I can’t get on with the treadmill, but I’ve gotten into running outside. I could live in activewear https://t.co/PX0jDEewv7
@laurakirsop I have also recently joined the gym for the first time ever and am surprised by how much I’m enjoying it! Even the weight machines!
@laurakirsop @khloekardashian I didn’t really understand what happened to me when i started running as a grown up. I never once successfully ran a complete lap of the school running track as a child
